Cell["\<\
This downloads RoBERTa, but you can alro use BERT, GPT2, CLIP or others. You \
might need to research how to get the best embeddings out.  \
https://resources.wolframcloud.com/NeuralNetRepository/\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9613107573379297`*^9, {3.9871679719522343`*^9, 3.9871680254235973`*^9}, {
