Cell["\<\
You can decide whether you want to read across all  your papers, or only \
around a term. If you input a term here, the reviewer only filters the \
sentences containing this term (case is ignored).This can be helpful if you \
want to write around a term you have aggregated the papers around, e.g. \
searchTerm=\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]Postmodernism\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]. \
Otherwise, just write searchTerm=None.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9613107573379297`*^9, {3.9871679719522343`*^9, 3.9871680254235973`*^9}, {
   3.987168233696315*^9, 3.9871682441454077`*^9}, {3.987169310388591*^9, 
