Cell["\<\
After compiling, save the file. You can navigate with the tiny triangles left \
and right to look for similar sentences in a band. All sentences link to the \
pages and documents where they are coming from in Zotero, and the \
attributions link to the item entry in your collection. Have fun reading! You \
can also export your file as a pdf for printing, links should still work but \
you only see the top sentence in the stack.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9613107573379297`*^9, {3.9871679719522343`*^9, 3.9871680254235973`*^9}, {
